title: Suggestion During Drive
text:
It's great map to use, one thing I can't stand is when it suggests another route in the middle of trip which can only save you 1 or 2 minutes. 1st of all what does a minute(or 2) save you when you are on 2 to 3hrs drive? Also the worse part of that is, it will minimize your map and asks you to accept or decline the the option, I find this is very dangerous especially when you are driving on highway with the speed of up to 60m/hr.
I hope google stop doing for the safety of drivers and their passengers.

title: National air LLC
text: if you’re looking for a dependable, professional, and knowledgeable company for your AC work then use National heating and cooling. Juan and his workers have been our go to guy for many of our house flips. What I like most about this company is I trust them. We thought a few times we would have to replace a unit but they said no this unit is fixable and we saved a lot of money. National heating and cooling keeps it simple and gives you options. So it came time that I needed to replace my 24-year-old AC. I knew I would use National Air but I did my homework and I got 6 estimates. National Air had the best prices by far and the install went perfect. They worked fast and were clean. So for all your AC needs pick up the phone and give this company a call. If TRUST is important to you then National heating and cooling is who you WANT!

title: What was the point?

title: I used google maps every day for work
text:
Hi Devs and Developers

I hope my message reaches you. Yall have always accepted and added my requested features. 

I’ve discovered another major inconvenience. When looking up and navigating to some stores or restaurants while trying to “add a stop” the location sometimes is INSIDE of a mall, college or private campus. There needs to be a flag or notification that this isn’t easily accessible or perhaps no drive through for fast food. 

Written:2018?
Hello, I’ve used your app everyday of my life for 9 years. Amazing and it’s made my life better. I drive to three different addresses a day to visit random customers all around my state. I use it to navigate to gas and food along the way. Some feedback I would like to request is to provide estimated cost for tolls on suggested routes. I’ve found that I’m out on toll roads for one exit making it almost pointless to enter a toll road. Or some option to only use toll roads if it saves me more than 10-20 minutes. There are also plenty of mislabeled exits. There should be a way to notify the app if there is a major issue that I run into daily where the gps puts me on the opposite side of the highway.
